ol.li:
        Notification: 

Form based workflow implemented with Java servlets and a custom designed MVC pattern
            for dealing with multilingual (Unicode - UTF8) data;

A complex mapping required a separate MS Access database to capture the specification
            and generate more than 400 templates;

Extensive use of Javascript to provide cross-browser dynamic HTML;

Authentication is made through an LDAP Database that synchronizes user profiles with
            the main Oracle database;

After processing, the data is exported to the SEI (Système Editorial Informatisé) in
            SGML. Later, an XML gateway is added.
